1
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:23,400
"Journey With You"

2
00:01:24,700 --> 00:01:26,700
(Episode 8)

3
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:42,168
Time passes so quickly.

4
00:01:42,836 --> 00:01:44,971
The day when the Emperor
asks you to return to Talhan

5
00:01:45,205 --> 00:01:46,606
is less than a month away.

6
00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:51,120
The Emperor has dealt with the remnants of the
Imperial Uncle's faction with lightning speed.

7
00:01:51,144 --> 00:01:52,922
There have been many
affairs in the court recently.

8
00:01:52,946 --> 00:01:54,180
As a prince,

9
00:01:54,647 --> 00:01:55,927
you've been working hard lately.

10
00:01:56,850 --> 00:01:58,151
The court ministers

11
00:01:58,485 --> 00:02:00,405
will also become more
and more convinced of you.

12
00:02:01,087 --> 00:02:02,088
I know.

13
00:02:03,022 --> 00:02:03,890
Before, in order to

14
00:02:03,891 --> 00:02:04,891
deal with Yinzhou,

15
00:02:04,958 --> 00:02:06,292
I used every means possible.

16
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:08,761
Now that Yinzhou is gone,

17
00:02:09,429 --> 00:02:12,065
I find doing these political
affairs utterly uninteresting.

18
00:02:14,667 --> 00:02:15,707
I understand how you feel.

19
00:02:16,703 --> 00:02:18,303
If you don't want to inherit the throne,

20
00:02:18,671 --> 00:02:20,871
then give more support to
your seventh younger brother.

21
00:02:21,107 --> 00:02:23,427
You also think the seventh
younger brother is good, right?

22
00:02:23,476 --> 00:02:25,156
We really have great chemistry between us.

23
00:02:32,085 --> 00:02:33,352
I've noticed that you

24
00:02:33,353 --> 00:02:34,753
haven't been looking well recently.

25
00:02:35,088 --> 00:02:36,088
Is it because

26
00:02:36,222 --> 00:02:38,662
I made you help with the
political affairs and you got tired?

27
00:02:39,826 --> 00:02:40,627
Speaking of which,

28
00:02:40,827 --> 00:02:41,860
Recently, Duan Yong and Duan Yi

29
00:02:41,861 --> 00:02:43,196
have also been extremely busy.

30
00:02:43,696 --> 00:02:45,231
Take a good rest next.

31
00:02:45,565 --> 00:02:47,267
I can handle the rest of the things alone.

32
00:02:50,036 --> 00:02:52,036
It's just that I want to
be with you all the time.

33
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,808
Before I leave the capital,

34
00:02:56,309 --> 00:02:58,687
I need to take care of some things
at the Piaoxiang Pavilion.

35
00:02:58,711 --> 00:02:59,812
This time when I leave,

36
00:03:02,715 --> 00:03:04,551
I don't know when I'll
be able to come back.

37
00:03:11,224 --> 00:03:12,224
By the way,

38
00:03:12,792 --> 00:03:13,792
The other day,

39
00:03:14,527 --> 00:03:16,428
I had a painter draw
portraits of the two of us.

40
00:03:16,429 --> 00:03:18,598
We'll each have one then.

41
00:03:20,667 --> 00:03:21,667
In consideration of

42
00:03:22,769 --> 00:03:25,004
how hard you've been working,

43
00:03:26,706 --> 00:03:28,408
I'll give you another gift.

44
00:03:37,103 --> 00:03:39,096
(Pei Yanzhi)

45
00:03:41,087 --> 00:03:42,087
This...

46
00:03:44,324 --> 00:03:45,390
When you return to the grasslands,

47
00:03:45,391 --> 00:03:46,793
everyone will call you Feng Sui.

48
00:03:47,260 --> 00:03:48,540
No one will call you Pei Yanzhi.

49
00:03:49,195 --> 00:03:50,597
I'm afraid that after a long time,

50
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,630
you'll forget.

51
00:03:55,501 --> 00:03:57,703
You should keep it close to you

52
00:03:57,704 --> 00:03:58,871
and think of me every day.

53
00:04:04,243 --> 00:04:05,243
Yanzhi,

54
00:04:05,645 --> 00:04:07,447
this name has a meaning.

55
00:04:08,381 --> 00:04:09,525
Grinding ink is silent, [Yan means
a kind of tool for grinding ink]

56
00:04:09,549 --> 00:04:11,751
yet it can write about
everything throughout the ages.

57
00:04:15,388 --> 00:04:16,689
The name you gave me,

58
00:04:18,257 --> 00:04:19,692
how could I dare to forget it?

59
00:04:28,067 --> 00:04:29,269
Although I know

60
00:04:29,969 --> 00:04:32,009
that you will definitely
come back after you leave,

61
00:04:32,071 --> 00:04:34,874
but the thought that once you leave,

62
00:04:35,008 --> 00:04:36,342
it might take several years,

63
00:04:36,709 --> 00:04:38,645
it makes my heart feel empty.

64
00:04:41,547 --> 00:04:42,547
A Qi,

65
00:04:43,283 --> 00:04:44,484
Before I leave,

66
00:04:44,717 --> 00:04:45,785
wherever you want to go,

67
00:04:45,885 --> 00:04:47,053
I'll go with you.

68
00:04:47,286 --> 00:04:49,822
Take it as my gift to you.

69
00:04:52,025 --> 00:04:53,025
Really?

70
00:05:00,867 --> 00:05:01,867
Look at this.

71
00:05:07,273 --> 00:05:07,940
Let's take this one.

72
00:05:07,941 --> 00:05:09,208
This is a good item.

73
00:05:09,609 --> 00:05:11,044
You have a good eye, miss.

74
00:05:11,678 --> 00:05:12,678
It smells so good.

75
00:05:16,496 --> 00:05:17,496
Yanzhi, come quickly.

76
00:05:17,550 --> 00:05:18,550
Come.

77
00:05:20,386 --> 00:05:21,386
Look.

78
00:05:21,554 --> 00:05:22,554
Look at this.

79
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:24,757
Duan Yi and Duan Yong,

80
00:05:24,957 --> 00:05:26,669
you two go back to the
Piaoxiang Pavilion and wait first.

81
00:05:26,693 --> 00:05:28,961
It's inconvenient to carry so many things.

82
00:05:29,362 --> 00:05:30,362
Yes.

83
00:05:30,663 --> 00:05:32,532
Please take your time. Come again.

84
00:05:32,965 --> 00:05:33,766
Those things

85
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,234
are all specialties of Daxing.

86
00:05:35,768 --> 00:05:37,888
You won't see them when
you return to the grasslands.

87
00:05:38,304 --> 00:05:41,453
I had the people in the palace
prepare many things for you too as well.

88
00:05:41,493 --> 00:05:43,542
When the time comes,
you should take them all.

89
00:05:44,477 --> 00:05:45,477
Okay, okay, okay.

90
00:05:45,745 --> 00:05:46,745
I'll listen to you.

91
00:05:49,482 --> 00:05:50,482
Let's go.

92
00:06:03,836 --> 00:06:04,836
Tell me,

93
00:06:05,798 --> 00:06:07,800
if you weren't the prince of Talhan

94
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,602
and I weren't a prince of Daxing,

95
00:06:10,570 --> 00:06:14,407
would we be as ordinary and happy as them?

96
00:06:17,844 --> 00:06:18,844
A Qi,

97
00:06:19,278 --> 00:06:20,680
No matter who you are

98
00:06:21,180 --> 00:06:22,348
or who you're with,

99
00:06:23,449 --> 00:06:24,650
you'll always be happy.

100
00:06:27,954 --> 00:06:29,355
It's because of you

101
00:06:29,555 --> 00:06:31,424
that I have a chance to start over.

102
00:06:32,558 --> 00:06:34,026
Without you,

103
00:06:35,595 --> 00:06:37,196
none of this would have happened.

104
00:06:38,865 --> 00:06:40,385
How could I even talk about happiness?

105
00:06:43,569 --> 00:06:44,837
So I'm that important.

106
00:06:46,372 --> 00:06:47,372
Let's go.

107
00:06:47,540 --> 00:06:48,820
Let's go take a look over there.

108
00:06:51,831 --> 00:06:52,265
Yanzhi,

109
00:06:52,478 --> 00:06:53,479
I've figured it out.

110
00:06:54,013 --> 00:06:55,648
When you come back from the grasslands,

111
00:06:55,915 --> 00:06:58,785
let's first travel all over the country.

112
00:06:59,452 --> 00:07:00,486
Then,

113
00:07:01,621 --> 00:07:02,889
and when we're old,

114
00:07:03,122 --> 00:07:04,590
let's settle down in Jiangnan.

115
00:07:04,690 --> 00:07:05,690
What do you think?

116
00:07:19,305 --> 00:07:20,106
Master,

117
00:07:20,173 --> 00:07:21,240
you're finally here.

118
00:07:22,141 --> 00:07:23,141
Fifth Prince,

119
00:07:25,331 --> 00:07:28,092
I've heard that the Red Dust Brew
at the Piaoxiang Pavilion is superb.

120
00:07:28,127 --> 00:07:30,325
I never had the mind to taste it
before when I came here.

121
00:07:30,349 --> 00:07:32,351
Today, I'm just here for leisure.

122
00:07:32,952 --> 00:07:33,985
My subordinates just received some

123
00:07:33,986 --> 00:07:34,954
secret letters from Talhan.

124
00:07:34,987 --> 00:07:36,222
They're about Su He.

125
00:07:36,289 --> 00:07:36,989
Master,

126
00:07:36,990 --> 00:07:38,200
come with me to the second floor first.

127
00:07:38,224 --> 00:07:39,601
I'll accompany the Fifth Prince later.

128
00:07:39,625 --> 00:07:40,359
Waiter,

129
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,161
bring a pot of Red
Dust Brew for this guest.

130
00:07:42,428 --> 00:07:42,795
Let's go.

131
00:07:42,795 --> 00:07:43,795
Okay.

132
00:07:43,996 --> 00:07:44,430
Come on,

133
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:44,931
sir,

134
00:07:44,931 --> 00:07:45,931
this way please.

135
00:07:55,708 --> 00:07:56,708
Master,

136
00:07:59,011 --> 00:08:00,011
Wenjie,

137
00:08:00,713 --> 00:08:01,713
help me.

138
00:08:01,981 --> 00:08:03,483
Okay, okay.

139
00:08:06,619 --> 00:08:07,619
Master,

140
00:08:08,387 --> 00:08:09,388
how are you now?

141
00:08:11,791 --> 00:08:12,791
It's okay.

142
00:08:13,292 --> 00:08:14,293
I can still hold on.

143
00:08:14,861 --> 00:08:16,261
You can hold on for a while,

144
00:08:16,262 --> 00:08:17,262
but...

145
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:25,671
this military token,

146
00:08:26,005 --> 00:08:27,606
have the accompanying secret envoy

147
00:08:27,607 --> 00:08:29,008
take it back to my eldest brother.

148
00:08:29,809 --> 00:08:30,809
Right now,

149
00:08:31,143 --> 00:08:32,478
without the threat of Su He,

150
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,514
I believe

151
00:08:37,617 --> 00:08:40,353
my eldest brother can
definitely govern Talhan very well.

152
00:08:43,556 --> 00:08:44,590
In this way,

153
00:08:46,292 --> 00:08:47,426
I'll be at ease.

154
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,395
Please don't say such things, Master.

155
00:08:50,196 --> 00:08:51,264
I don't believe

156
00:08:51,597 --> 00:08:53,266
the poison in your body can't be cured.

157
00:08:53,833 --> 00:08:55,668
Why not tell the Fifth Prince about this?

158
00:08:55,801 --> 00:08:56,869
As a prince,

159
00:08:57,003 --> 00:08:58,604
he can find any famous doctor.

160
00:09:00,907 --> 00:09:02,341
If it can be cured,

161
00:09:03,042 --> 00:09:04,644
how could I just sit and wait for death?

162
00:09:08,147 --> 00:09:09,147
But

163
00:09:11,336 --> 00:09:12,336
in this life,

164
00:09:13,853 --> 00:09:17,023
I've been able to help
A Qi clear away obstacles

165
00:09:18,391 --> 00:09:22,194
and help my eldest brother
eliminate treacherous officials.

166
00:09:25,765 --> 00:09:27,567
I have no regrets.

167
00:09:30,236 --> 00:09:33,839
But you've sacrificed
yourself for everyone.

168
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,275
I think it's not worth it.

169
00:09:37,710 --> 00:09:39,345
Because in my eyes,

170
00:09:40,913 --> 00:09:42,281
you are the most important.

171
00:09:45,351 --> 00:09:46,351
Wenjie,

172
00:09:47,486 --> 00:09:50,590
It's been an honor to

173
00:09:52,124 --> 00:09:53,559
work with you in this life.

174
00:09:55,247 --> 00:09:56,281
If you

175
00:09:57,697 --> 00:09:59,999
still remember the affection between us,

176
00:10:07,306 --> 00:10:08,674
I have a request.

177
00:10:09,542 --> 00:10:10,542
Master,

178
00:10:11,310 --> 00:10:12,511
just tell me.

179
00:10:13,245 --> 00:10:14,847
I'll do my utmost.

180
00:10:16,248 --> 00:10:17,450
If one day,

181
00:10:19,318 --> 00:10:20,786
A Qi encounters difficulties,

182
00:10:30,563 --> 00:10:31,964
you must help him.

183
00:10:34,634 --> 00:10:35,634
Okay.

184
00:10:36,168 --> 00:10:37,168
Okay.

185
00:10:52,351 --> 00:10:54,353
Aren't you about to return to Talhan?

186
00:10:54,620 --> 00:10:56,222
Why are you still so busy with things?

187
00:10:56,689 --> 00:10:57,490
By the way,

188
00:10:57,491 --> 00:10:59,692
this Red Dust Brew is really delicious.

189
00:10:59,792 --> 00:11:00,993
No wonder it's so famous.

190
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:09,100
Waiter,

191
00:11:09,502 --> 00:11:10,502
bring a pot of warm wine.

192
00:11:10,803 --> 00:11:11,803
Okay.

193
00:11:18,711 --> 00:11:20,279
You always like to drink cold wine.

194
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:25,151
You'll get a headache the next day
if you drink too much.

195
00:11:29,021 --> 00:11:30,021
In the future,

196
00:11:30,523 --> 00:11:31,957
when I'm not by your side,

197
00:11:33,959 --> 00:11:35,479
you should take good care of yourself.

198
00:11:37,163 --> 00:11:38,631
Take good care of your body.

199
00:11:40,399 --> 00:11:41,801
Don't drink cold wine anymore.

200
00:11:44,837 --> 00:11:47,173
Your tribesmen must not know this,

201
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:50,042
that their Feng Sun Prince
who gallops across the grasslands

202
00:11:50,076 --> 00:11:51,877
has such a fussy side.

203
00:11:52,511 --> 00:11:53,279
Don't worry.

204
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:55,081
I'll take good care of myself for you.

205
00:11:55,281 --> 00:11:56,614
I definitely won't give you a chance

206
00:11:56,615 --> 00:11:58,655
to dislike me for being
three years older than you.

207
00:12:03,923 --> 00:12:05,603
Why have you lost so much weight recently?

208
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:06,926
Come on,

209
00:12:06,926 --> 00:12:07,926
eat more.

210
00:12:53,307 --> 00:12:56,174
(Yin Qi)

211
00:13:03,582 --> 00:13:05,151
I thought you were as hard as a rock,

212
00:13:05,451 --> 00:13:07,820
not showing any reluctance for so long.

213
00:13:08,354 --> 00:13:09,354
I didn't expect

214
00:13:12,224 --> 00:13:13,224
it was all an act.

215
00:13:20,232 --> 00:13:21,567
I've lived here for ten years,

216
00:13:22,034 --> 00:13:23,402
almost half of my life.

217
00:13:24,436 --> 00:13:25,638
How could I let go?

218
00:13:27,473 --> 00:13:28,807
How old are you?

219
00:13:29,508 --> 00:13:32,211
We still have the rest
of our lives together.

220
00:13:37,183 --> 00:13:38,183
Speaking of which,

221
00:13:39,652 --> 00:13:41,732
I haven't been to the
Yonghe Palace for a long time.

222
00:13:45,724 --> 00:13:47,364
The last time I came to the Yonghe Palace

223
00:13:48,327 --> 00:13:50,462
was after sending my
mother back to Jiangnan.

224
00:13:51,564 --> 00:13:52,765
During that time,

225
00:13:53,933 --> 00:13:55,968
I haven't dared to come
to my mother's residence,

226
00:13:56,969 --> 00:13:58,470
afraid that a single mistake

227
00:13:58,904 --> 00:14:00,639
would prevent me from changing our fates.

228
00:14:02,408 --> 00:14:03,876
I'd have no face to face my mother.

229
00:14:08,913 --> 00:14:11,153
Even if you didn't change the outcome
of your past life,

230
00:14:11,650 --> 00:14:13,252
Concubine Chen wouldn't blame you.

231
00:14:25,231 --> 00:14:26,232
There's something.

232
00:14:28,367 --> 00:14:30,169
I haven't told you and Heshu.

233
00:14:31,837 --> 00:14:35,040
Actually, before my mother left,

234
00:14:36,488 --> 00:14:37,728
it seemed like she sensed that

235
00:14:38,310 --> 00:14:40,045
I had come back from my past life.

236
00:14:42,848 --> 00:14:43,883
At that time,

237
00:14:46,719 --> 00:14:47,719
she even touched

238
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:49,188
the place where I was shot

239
00:14:49,755 --> 00:14:50,889
and asked if it hurt.

240
00:14:55,261 --> 00:14:57,062
I only figured it out later.

241
00:14:57,863 --> 00:14:58,863
Perhaps

242
00:15:00,032 --> 00:15:02,868
my mother and I have a
deep mother-son bond.

243
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:09,541
Concubine Chen

244
00:15:09,608 --> 00:15:11,243
was afraid that after she left,

245
00:15:11,610 --> 00:15:12,930
you would be bullied by Yin Zhou.

246
00:15:14,780 --> 00:15:15,780
By the way, A Qi,

247
00:15:16,248 --> 00:15:17,383
do you remember

248
00:15:17,583 --> 00:15:19,251
the last time we were here?

249
00:15:20,586 --> 00:15:21,586
A Qi,

250
00:15:22,087 --> 00:15:23,088
the last time you said

251
00:15:23,749 --> 00:15:25,749
to secretly send Concubine
Chen out of the palace.

252
00:15:26,171 --> 00:15:27,171
But why me?

253
00:15:27,326 --> 00:15:28,326
You're right.

254
00:15:28,594 --> 00:15:29,962
It was too risky.

255
00:15:30,930 --> 00:15:33,165
I shouldn't have risked
my mother's body either.

256
00:15:34,366 --> 00:15:35,768
At that time, the two of us

257
00:15:36,035 --> 00:15:37,569
had our own hidden agendas

258
00:15:37,836 --> 00:15:39,180
and wouldn't give in to each other.

259
00:15:39,204 --> 00:15:40,615
Neither knew what
the other was thinking

260
00:15:40,639 --> 00:15:41,839
or what they were going to do.

261
00:15:42,675 --> 00:15:44,543
If it weren't for my persistence,

262
00:15:45,611 --> 00:15:48,280
with your stubborn temperament of
not wanting to speak up,

263
00:15:48,681 --> 00:15:50,449
even if I lived ten more lives,

264
00:15:50,683 --> 00:15:52,685
I might not be able to change our fate.

265
00:16:08,767 --> 00:16:10,202
After I leave the capital,

266
00:16:15,074 --> 00:16:16,542
you must be very careful.

267
00:16:17,409 --> 00:16:18,811
Don't trust anyone,

268
00:16:19,478 --> 00:16:20,478
just like

269
00:16:22,414 --> 00:16:23,682
you were wary of me before.

270
00:16:25,724 --> 00:16:26,892
I've remembered it all.

271
00:16:28,287 --> 00:16:30,556
Why are you even more
worried about me than my mother?

272
00:16:53,912 --> 00:16:54,980
A Qi,

273
00:16:55,914 --> 00:16:56,954
Don't send me any further.

274
00:16:57,783 --> 00:16:58,783
If you send me further,

275
00:16:59,885 --> 00:17:01,653
you won't make it into the city before dark.

276
00:17:02,955 --> 00:17:03,955
But

277
00:17:04,089 --> 00:17:05,529
I want to see you off a bit further.

278
00:17:11,330 --> 00:17:12,431
If you keep sending me off,

279
00:17:12,931 --> 00:17:15,131
you'll end up sending me
all the way to the grasslands.

280
00:17:16,035 --> 00:17:16,802
Okay.

281
00:17:16,803 --> 00:17:18,003
I'll listen to you.

282
00:17:18,203 --> 00:17:19,605
But you have to promise me.

283
00:17:19,638 --> 00:17:20,472
Come back as soon as possible.

284
00:17:20,506 --> 00:17:21,607
The sooner, the better.

285
00:17:22,508 --> 00:17:23,508
And also,

286
00:17:23,742 --> 00:17:25,210
remember to write to me.

287
00:17:25,244 --> 00:17:27,346
I'll wait for your letters every day.

288
00:17:30,315 --> 00:17:31,315
I promise you.

289
00:20:28,147 --> 00:20:30,267
(Concubine Chen's Gravestone)

290
00:20:30,395 --> 00:20:31,395
Concubine Chen,

291
00:20:32,864 --> 00:20:33,864
I promised you.

292
00:20:34,232 --> 00:20:35,634
I've finally done it.

293
00:20:37,369 --> 00:20:38,369
Now,

294
00:20:43,942 --> 00:20:45,844
no one can stop A Qi

295
00:20:45,877 --> 00:20:47,412
from living the life he wants.

296
00:21:05,163 --> 00:21:06,565
But thinking carefully,

297
00:21:11,770 --> 00:21:15,007
I seem to have failed to
live up to your instructions.

298
00:21:17,075 --> 00:21:18,075
I promised

299
00:21:19,478 --> 00:21:21,013
to protect A Qi for a lifetime.

300
00:21:25,150 --> 00:21:28,787
Now I might have to break that promise.

301
00:21:34,593 --> 00:21:35,994
When I see you again,

302
00:21:37,329 --> 00:21:38,730
I'll apologize to you in person.

303
00:22:18,970 --> 00:22:19,970
Yanzhi,

304
00:22:20,372 --> 00:22:21,372
Yanzhi,

305
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,607
why are you here?

306
00:22:24,456 --> 00:22:25,456
Yanzhi,

307
00:22:25,711 --> 00:22:26,711
wake up!

308
00:22:40,959 --> 00:22:41,959
Come here.

309
00:22:42,127 --> 00:22:43,127
Aunt Lin,

310
00:22:50,035 --> 00:22:51,103
This is Yanbo Tower.

311
00:22:53,405 --> 00:22:54,439
Why am I here?

312
00:22:55,207 --> 00:22:56,475
I was going to ask you that.

313
00:22:57,008 --> 00:22:59,044
Didn't you go back to
the capital with Qi'er?

314
00:22:59,845 --> 00:23:02,085
How did you end up fainting
in front of Tang'er's grave?

315
00:23:07,385 --> 00:23:09,888
This palace is truly no place for humans.

316
00:23:10,622 --> 00:23:12,391
Yin Zhou is so vicious.

317
00:23:13,759 --> 00:23:15,160
So according to you,

318
00:23:15,861 --> 00:23:17,996
Qi'er knows nothing about your poisoning.

319
00:23:20,198 --> 00:23:21,333
A Qi has

320
00:23:22,901 --> 00:23:24,436
a long road ahead of him.

321
00:23:25,403 --> 00:23:26,772
If he finds out,

322
00:23:27,606 --> 00:23:29,408
it'll be a heavy blow to him.

323
00:23:31,843 --> 00:23:32,344
One day,

324
00:23:32,345 --> 00:23:33,812
he'll get used to living without me.

325
00:23:35,347 --> 00:23:37,549
Qi'er is a sentimental child.

326
00:23:38,583 --> 00:23:40,185
He said he'd wait for you.

327
00:23:40,919 --> 00:23:41,919
What if

328
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:43,789
he really waits for you his whole life?

329
00:23:44,523 --> 00:23:45,690
If he's willing to wait,

330
00:23:47,993 --> 00:23:49,793
at least he has something
to look forward to.

331
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:53,131
If he knows the whole truth,

332
00:23:54,199 --> 00:23:55,400
it'll only make him suffer.

333
00:23:57,569 --> 00:24:00,405
My name, Lin Jianshuang,
isn't for nothing.

334
00:24:00,872 --> 00:24:01,872
You can rest assured.

335
00:24:02,274 --> 00:24:04,209
Even if I have to search the whole country,

336
00:24:04,409 --> 00:24:06,444
I'll definitely cure the
poison in your body.

337
00:24:07,946 --> 00:24:10,449
Just stay at Yanbo Tower peacefully.

338
00:24:10,749 --> 00:24:11,749
Aunt Lin,

339
00:24:12,451 --> 00:24:13,451
In this life,

340
00:24:14,386 --> 00:24:15,386
being able to accompany A Qi

341
00:24:15,387 --> 00:24:17,227
through the most
important journey of his life

342
00:24:17,622 --> 00:24:18,790
is enough for me.

343
00:24:24,062 --> 00:24:24,563
By the way,

344
00:24:24,563 --> 00:24:25,363
Aunt Lin,

345
00:24:25,530 --> 00:24:28,366
could you please get me
some writing materials?

346
00:24:28,567 --> 00:24:30,769
I promised to write to A Qi.

347
00:24:32,170 --> 00:24:33,170
Okay.

348
00:24:42,147 --> 00:24:43,147
Aunt Lin,

349
00:24:43,448 --> 00:24:45,383
please give this letter to A Qi for me.

350
00:24:46,318 --> 00:24:48,053
He'll be at ease after receiving it.

351
00:24:48,420 --> 00:24:49,420
Okay.

352
00:24:50,021 --> 00:24:51,021
Brother Yanzhi,

353
00:24:51,523 --> 00:24:52,324
You've finished

354
00:24:52,325 --> 00:24:53,885
dealing with palace affairs so quickly.

355
00:24:53,925 --> 00:24:55,965
Why didn't you tell me you
were coming to Jiangnan?

356
00:24:56,455 --> 00:24:57,455
Where's my royal brother?

357
00:24:57,796 --> 00:24:58,597
Where is he?

358
00:24:58,797 --> 00:24:59,797
It's just me.

359
00:24:59,931 --> 00:25:00,799
A Qi didn't come.

360
00:25:00,799 --> 00:25:01,799
I want to

361
00:25:02,467 --> 00:25:03,435
go back to Talhan.

362
00:25:03,468 --> 00:25:04,468
I'm just passing by here.

363
00:25:05,103 --> 00:25:06,605
Don't tell your royal brother.

364
00:25:08,740 --> 00:25:09,740
I

365
00:25:10,642 --> 00:25:11,642
I'm

366
00:25:11,743 --> 00:25:12,878
suffering from a cold.

367
00:25:13,111 --> 00:25:14,212
I'm afraid it'll worry him.

368
00:25:26,291 --> 00:25:27,291
Wen Jie,

369
00:25:27,425 --> 00:25:29,194
I received a letter from Yanzhi.

370
00:25:30,362 --> 00:25:31,963
Master sent a letter so quickly.

371
00:25:32,664 --> 00:25:34,966
He must be close to Talhan by now.

372
00:25:35,967 --> 00:25:37,044
He was in a hurry on the way,

373
00:25:37,068 --> 00:25:37,802
so he only had time

374
00:25:37,803 --> 00:25:39,547
to send this letter to
let us know he's safe.

375
00:25:39,571 --> 00:25:40,681
He's afraid you'll worry about him.

376
00:25:40,705 --> 00:25:41,705
He asked me to tell you

377
00:25:41,706 --> 00:25:42,741
that he's doing fine.

378
00:25:43,141 --> 00:25:44,141
Okay.

379
00:25:44,743 --> 00:25:45,743
As long as he's safe.

380
00:25:48,246 --> 00:25:49,581
You seem strange.

381
00:25:50,225 --> 00:25:52,894
Yanzhi will come back to Daxing
after finishing things this time.

382
00:25:52,918 --> 00:25:53,919
It won't be long.

383
00:25:54,719 --> 00:25:56,788
What if Master

384
00:25:57,355 --> 00:25:58,590
takes many years this time?

385
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:02,960
With Yanzhi's abilities,

386
00:26:02,961 --> 00:26:03,971
he'll definitely come
back within three years.

387
00:26:03,995 --> 00:26:05,196
He will definitely come back.

388
00:26:05,597 --> 00:26:06,398
What's wrong?

389
00:26:06,531 --> 00:26:08,033
Don't you trust your lord?

390
00:26:31,589 --> 00:26:32,600
What are you thinking about?

391
00:26:32,624 --> 00:26:33,792
You're absent-minded.

392
00:26:37,529 --> 00:26:38,530
I'm wondering

393
00:26:39,264 --> 00:26:41,966
why Brother Yanzhi always tells me

394
00:26:41,967 --> 00:26:43,067
not to tell my royal brother

395
00:26:43,068 --> 00:26:44,436
about him being at Yanbo Tower.

396
00:26:45,370 --> 00:26:46,871
If he just wants to rest,

397
00:26:47,172 --> 00:26:47,839
then why

398
00:26:47,840 --> 00:26:49,007
can't my royal brother know?

399
00:26:50,909 --> 00:26:52,042
You also think Brother Yanzhi's

400
00:26:52,043 --> 00:26:53,603
visit to Jiangnan this time is strange.

401
00:26:54,713 --> 00:26:56,680
The other day, I saw
my aunt bring a stranger

402
00:26:56,681 --> 00:26:58,583
into Brother Yanzhi's room.

403
00:26:58,750 --> 00:27:00,790
But when I asked my aunt
who that person was later,

404
00:27:01,052 --> 00:27:02,587
she wouldn't tell me anything.

405
00:27:08,727 --> 00:27:09,727
It seems like

406
00:27:09,794 --> 00:27:11,262
we need to think of a way.

407
00:27:15,667 --> 00:27:16,667
Yes.

408
00:27:16,901 --> 00:27:18,003
Hold the hilt like this,

409
00:27:23,508 --> 00:27:24,508
thrust it out.

410
00:27:27,245 --> 00:27:29,648
Good job, good job!

411
00:27:30,515 --> 00:27:32,117
Zhou'er is going to ascend the throne.

412
00:27:32,484 --> 00:27:33,985
I'm going to be the Empress Dowager.

413
00:27:34,486 --> 00:27:36,287
Zhou'er is going to ascend the throne.

414
00:27:36,755 --> 00:27:38,356
Concubine Chen is also dead.

415
00:27:38,577 --> 00:27:41,312
I killed Concubine Chen.

416
00:27:42,394 --> 00:27:43,954
What do you mean by what you just said?

417
00:27:44,562 --> 00:27:47,065
Did you kill my mother?

418
00:27:48,306 --> 00:27:49,574
During the hunt,

419
00:27:50,194 --> 00:27:52,396
she insisted on drinking your wine.

420
00:27:53,271 --> 00:27:54,639
Since she wanted to die,

421
00:27:55,113 --> 00:27:56,714
I let her die.

422
00:27:58,810 --> 00:28:00,612
Explain it clearly to me.

423
00:28:01,299 --> 00:28:04,502
What exactly happened
at the hunting ground?

424
00:28:11,389 --> 00:28:12,424
Strange.

425
00:28:12,557 --> 00:28:13,558
It's really strange.

426
00:28:14,959 --> 00:28:15,959
How?

427
00:28:17,796 --> 00:28:19,230
According to my diagnosis,

428
00:28:19,564 --> 00:28:21,764
the young master should
have contracted a cold illness.

429
00:28:22,033 --> 00:28:23,468
If we're talking about poisoning,

430
00:28:23,768 --> 00:28:25,370
then there's only one possibility.

431
00:28:25,804 --> 00:28:27,872
This poison can penetrate
the internal organs,

432
00:28:28,245 --> 00:28:29,580
causing a cold illness

433
00:28:29,874 --> 00:28:31,009
and death from coughing.

434
00:28:33,244 --> 00:28:34,244
Cold illness.

435
00:28:35,453 --> 00:28:36,453
Coughing.

436
00:28:40,452 --> 00:28:41,453
Concubine Chen,

437
00:28:45,990 --> 00:28:47,191
My mother was poisoned.

438
00:28:49,728 --> 00:28:51,029
I remember now.

439
00:28:51,563 --> 00:28:52,964
Your young master

440
00:28:53,331 --> 00:28:54,766
won't survive either.

441
00:28:54,846 --> 00:28:56,381
What have you done to Yanzhi again?

442
00:28:56,901 --> 00:28:58,045
Your Royal Highness, the Fifth Prince,

443
00:28:58,069 --> 00:28:59,346
ever since the Crown Prince passed away,

444
00:28:59,370 --> 00:29:00,839
the Empress has been acting crazy.

445
00:29:00,863 --> 00:29:02,457
You can't take her words seriously.

446
00:29:02,481 --> 00:29:03,743
He won't survive either.

447
00:29:07,746 --> 00:29:08,746
I didn't expect

448
00:29:11,082 --> 00:29:12,516
that Tang'er and you

449
00:29:12,517 --> 00:29:13,917
were poisoned with the same poison.

450
00:29:15,053 --> 00:29:16,053
Doctor,

451
00:29:16,087 --> 00:29:17,555
is there a way to cure it?

452
00:29:18,723 --> 00:29:21,092
I've never seen this poison before.

453
00:29:21,359 --> 00:29:24,062
I can only prescribe some medicine
to relieve the coughing pain.

454
00:29:24,662 --> 00:29:25,797
As for curing it,

455
00:29:26,164 --> 00:29:27,832
I really can't do it.

456
00:29:29,501 --> 00:29:30,501
Doctor,

457
00:29:32,303 --> 00:29:33,638
how long do I have left?

458
00:29:34,171 --> 00:29:35,740
The young master is physically strong.

459
00:29:36,074 --> 00:29:38,042
With medicine to delay the onset,

460
00:29:38,209 --> 00:29:40,011
he might live for three months.

461
00:29:48,119 --> 00:29:49,519
I'm going to tell my royal brother.

462
00:30:03,334 --> 00:30:04,334
What's wrong with Yanzhi?

463
00:30:04,536 --> 00:30:05,470
What exactly is wrong with Yanzhi?

464
00:30:05,471 --> 00:30:06,471
Tell me quickly.

465
00:30:06,971 --> 00:30:07,971
You,

466
00:30:08,239 --> 00:30:09,240
you already know...?

467
00:30:09,874 --> 00:30:11,209
What do you mean he's dying?

468
00:30:11,709 --> 00:30:13,478
Tell me everything you know quickly.

469
00:30:13,658 --> 00:30:14,663
When Master was in Jiangnan,

470
00:30:14,687 --> 00:30:16,087
Yin Zhou poisoned him.

471
00:30:17,282 --> 00:30:18,362
He was afraid you'd be sad,

472
00:30:18,550 --> 00:30:19,910
so he told us not to say anything.

473
00:30:20,318 --> 00:30:21,553
How did you find out?

474
00:30:22,287 --> 00:30:23,727
He didn't go back to the grasslands.

475
00:30:24,389 --> 00:30:25,389
Where is he?

476
00:30:25,957 --> 00:30:27,158
I don't know.

477
00:30:27,625 --> 00:30:28,903
Your Royal Highness, the Fifth Prince,

478
00:30:28,927 --> 00:30:30,962
I advise you not to
look for Master anymore.

479
00:30:31,629 --> 00:30:32,997
He doesn't want you to know,

480
00:30:33,031 --> 00:30:35,366
precisely because he doesn't
want you to to watch him die.

481
00:30:35,987 --> 00:30:37,307
He's been struggling for his life

482
00:30:37,635 --> 00:30:39,636
just so you can live peacefully.

483
00:30:39,637 --> 00:30:40,371
Why can't you just

484
00:30:40,371 --> 00:30:41,371
fulfill his wish?

485
00:30:42,206 --> 00:30:43,306
If he dies,

486
00:30:43,330 --> 00:30:44,398
how can I live peacefully?

487
00:30:46,411 --> 00:30:47,478
Anyway, I don't know.

488
00:30:47,745 --> 00:30:49,080
It's useless to press me.

489
00:30:49,581 --> 00:30:51,049
I'll definitely find out.

490
00:31:01,739 --> 00:31:02,373
Your Royal Highness,

491
00:31:02,560 --> 00:31:03,394
where is Yanzhi?

492
00:31:03,461 --> 00:31:04,462
Any news?

493
00:31:05,997 --> 00:31:08,442
The young master seems to
have deliberately hidden his whereabouts.

494
00:31:08,466 --> 00:31:10,786
No post stations along the way
have seen the young master.

495
00:31:12,503 --> 00:31:13,104
Your Royal Highness,

496
00:31:13,204 --> 00:31:15,084
I've received a letter
from the Sixth Princess.

497
00:31:21,446 --> 00:31:23,447
Should I go and persuade
Your Royal Highness?

498
00:31:23,448 --> 00:31:24,916
I think it's better not.

499
00:31:25,617 --> 00:31:26,451
Royal brother,

500
00:31:26,452 --> 00:31:27,751
Pei Yanzhi has been poisoned deeply.

501
00:31:27,752 --> 00:31:28,620
He doesn't have long to live.

502
00:31:28,621 --> 00:31:30,581
I hope the Fifth Royal
Brother will come quickly.

503
00:31:30,755 --> 00:31:31,755
Yanzhi,

504
00:31:32,023 --> 00:31:33,024
Yanzhi is in Jiangnan.

505
00:31:34,893 --> 00:31:35,693
Duan Yong,

506
00:31:35,793 --> 00:31:37,061
hurry and tell Doctor Bai

507
00:31:37,161 --> 00:31:38,563
to come with me to Jiangnan.

508
00:31:39,330 --> 00:31:40,330
Go to Jiangnan again?

509
00:31:40,565 --> 00:31:42,634
Isn't the young master in the grasslands?

510
00:31:42,667 --> 00:31:43,677
Don't ask so many questions.

511
00:31:43,701 --> 00:31:44,469
Hurry and go.

512
00:31:44,469 --> 00:31:45,469
Don't delay.

513
00:31:46,204 --> 00:31:46,638
Yes.

514
00:31:46,671 --> 00:31:47,671
Yes.

515
00:31:51,442 --> 00:31:52,477
What did you say?

516
00:31:52,877 --> 00:31:54,245
You're going to Jiangnan.

517
00:31:55,647 --> 00:31:57,048
Just for that hostage.

518
00:31:59,717 --> 00:32:02,287
Yanzhi is the only
person I cherish in my life.

519
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:04,298
The one I want to spend
the rest of my life with.

520
00:32:04,322 --> 00:32:06,333
We've already pledged our
eternal love to each other.

521
00:32:06,357 --> 00:32:07,997
Promising to never part in this lifetime.

522
00:32:08,559 --> 00:32:11,963
So I must go to Jiangnan to save him.

523
00:32:12,423 --> 00:32:13,423
How dare you!

524
00:32:15,700 --> 00:32:16,501
Qi'er.

525
00:32:16,701 --> 00:32:18,703
You've disappointed me greatly.

526
00:32:19,170 --> 00:32:21,673
You know very well that
after your eldest royal brother left.

527
00:32:21,873 --> 00:32:24,409
You're the only prince I can rely on.

528
00:32:24,642 --> 00:32:26,611
Yet you're so stubborn and unenlightened.

529
00:32:27,512 --> 00:32:29,580
You've not only disappointed me.

530
00:32:30,234 --> 00:32:32,984
But also the entire Daxing Kingdom.

531
00:32:38,582 --> 00:32:39,582
Father.

532
00:32:40,091 --> 00:32:42,359
Please forgive my words today, for speaking out of turn.

533
00:32:43,027 --> 00:32:45,063
But I want to tell you, Father.

534
00:32:45,709 --> 00:32:47,269
You're still in the prime of your life,

535
00:32:47,612 --> 00:32:49,766
with plenty of time to groom the Seventh Prince.

536
00:32:50,234 --> 00:32:52,804
The future ten or twenty years of Daxing

537
00:32:52,828 --> 00:32:54,188
will always belong to you, Father.

538
00:32:55,506 --> 00:32:56,841
As for me.

539
00:32:58,109 --> 00:33:00,311
You can demote me to a commoner

540
00:33:00,345 --> 00:33:01,546
I have no complaints.

541
00:33:02,847 --> 00:33:03,847
Rebellious son.

542
00:33:03,948 --> 00:33:04,948
Rebellious son.

543
00:33:05,350 --> 00:33:08,686
Do you really think Daxing can't
survive without a prince like you?

544
00:33:08,953 --> 00:33:10,521
Come back to me!

545
00:33:10,788 --> 00:33:11,788
Come back!

546
00:33:39,984 --> 00:33:40,785
Yanzhi.

547
00:33:40,985 --> 00:33:41,985
You're awake.

548
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:44,020
A Qi.

549
00:33:44,355 --> 00:33:45,355
What are you...

550
00:33:51,396 --> 00:33:52,430
Where am I?

551
00:33:52,797 --> 00:33:54,031
I asked Doctor Bai.

552
00:33:54,599 --> 00:33:57,602
He said the hot springs at the
imperial palace are good for your health.

553
00:33:58,069 --> 00:33:59,984
So I brought you from Yanbo Tower back here.

554
00:34:03,708 --> 00:34:05,009
You know now.

555
00:34:08,713 --> 00:34:09,713
So.

556
00:34:10,548 --> 00:34:17,955
Before you left the capital, The
words you said to me were all farewells.

557
00:34:29,067 --> 00:34:30,067
A Qi.

558
00:34:34,405 --> 00:34:35,740
You shouldn't have come here.

559
00:34:36,207 --> 00:34:37,742
Now is not the time for this.

560
00:34:38,242 --> 00:34:39,043
Yanzhi.

561
00:34:39,083 --> 00:34:40,184
Trust me.

562
00:34:40,244 --> 00:34:42,013
I'll definitely find a way to cure you.

563
00:34:44,148 --> 00:34:45,148
A Qi.

564
00:34:45,483 --> 00:34:46,483
A Qi.

565
00:34:46,884 --> 00:34:47,884
A Qi.

566
00:34:56,394 --> 00:34:57,394
You're crazy.

567
00:34:58,629 --> 00:35:00,031
This is your plan?

568
00:35:00,431 --> 00:35:01,431
To die?

569
00:35:02,366 --> 00:35:05,629
Only if I die will the gods
give me another chance.

570
00:35:05,803 --> 00:35:07,772
What if the gods don't
give you another chance?

571
00:35:10,675 --> 00:35:12,043
Then you'll drown.

572
00:35:21,071 --> 00:35:23,497
Have you forgotten all the
hardships we've faced on our journey?

573
00:35:23,521 --> 00:35:24,521
If you...

574
00:35:27,024 --> 00:35:28,392
if you really die,

575
00:35:30,194 --> 00:35:31,863
will you be able to face Concubine Chen?

576
00:35:31,886 --> 00:35:33,721
Can't I just give up on my own life?

577
00:35:39,670 --> 00:35:40,670
Yanzhi.

578
00:35:43,007 --> 00:35:44,007
What should I do?

579
00:35:52,316 --> 00:35:56,220
Don't place your hopes on such things.

580
00:36:01,792 --> 00:36:02,792
A Qi.

581
00:36:03,528 --> 00:36:04,562
Come back with me.

582
00:36:05,396 --> 00:36:06,998
Or you'll catch a cold.

583
00:36:13,004 --> 00:36:14,972
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

584
00:36:15,806 --> 00:36:17,542
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

585
00:36:20,278 --> 00:36:21,278
Why?

586
00:36:23,381 --> 00:36:25,149
I don't want you to leave me.

587
00:36:25,783 --> 00:36:26,783
I don't want it.

588
00:36:41,666 --> 00:36:43,067
Have some hot water.

589
00:36:43,434 --> 00:36:44,802
You've been outside for so long.

590
00:36:45,202 --> 00:36:46,202
Don't catch a cold.

591
00:37:12,730 --> 00:37:14,165
How could you be so foolish?

592
00:37:18,703 --> 00:37:20,304
Do you really believe

593
00:37:22,006 --> 00:37:23,806
the eternal gods will
give us another chance?

594
00:37:24,675 --> 00:37:26,010
Of course I believe.

595
00:37:31,749 --> 00:37:33,651
I won't give up easily.

596
00:37:36,087 --> 00:37:38,289
I'll definitely find a way to save you.

597
00:37:44,629 --> 00:37:46,364
Our A Qi has really grown up.

598
00:37:49,567 --> 00:37:50,567
Masterminding strategies.

599
00:37:50,968 --> 00:37:51,969
Never giving up.

600
00:37:57,074 --> 00:37:58,943
Increasingly resembling a crown prince.

601
00:38:01,145 --> 00:38:03,247
You never consider my feelings.

602
00:38:03,948 --> 00:38:11,282
Do you think that after you leave I
can just pretend that nothing happened?

603
00:38:11,789 --> 00:38:13,991
And I can continue
being the Fifth Prince?

604
00:38:24,802 --> 00:38:25,802
I'm sorry.

605
00:38:30,274 --> 00:38:31,676
I couldn't think of a better way.

606
00:38:38,349 --> 00:38:40,351
I didn't want you to see me like this now.

607
00:38:45,890 --> 00:38:46,890
I want...

608
00:38:48,926 --> 00:38:49,926
my A Qi...

609
00:38:54,932 --> 00:38:56,100
to be happy.

610
00:39:16,587 --> 00:39:17,587
Your Highness

611
00:39:18,389 --> 00:39:20,767
I've been browsing through
ancient texts these past few days.

612
00:39:20,791 --> 00:39:24,161
And discovered that there is indeed a
strange poison in Japan called Amantuo.

613
00:39:24,795 --> 00:39:27,998
This poison is strange in that
it doesn't kill immediately,

614
00:39:28,232 --> 00:39:29,600
but slowly takes effect,

615
00:39:29,834 --> 00:39:31,674
rventually causing death
by coughing up blood.

616
00:39:32,770 --> 00:39:37,541
The whole process looks like contracting a
severe cold and dying from an incurable illness.

617
00:39:39,009 --> 00:39:43,080
The symptoms of Concubine
Chen and the young master all match up.

618
00:39:50,087 --> 00:39:51,087
Nan Xing.

619
00:39:51,689 --> 00:39:52,689
You...

620
00:39:53,324 --> 00:39:54,324
do you have a way?

621
00:39:58,396 --> 00:39:59,396
A Qi.

622
00:40:00,097 --> 00:40:01,499
Since I came to Jiangnan.

623
00:40:02,333 --> 00:40:04,668
Aunt Lin has found many famous doctors to treat me.

624
00:40:06,036 --> 00:40:09,632
Each doctor has said that they don't
know how to detoxify this poison.

625
00:40:11,609 --> 00:40:12,609
A Qi.

626
00:40:17,982 --> 00:40:20,731
I indeed have no way to detoxify it.

627
00:40:21,252 --> 00:40:22,612
I can only follow the prescription

628
00:40:22,787 --> 00:40:24,227
to regulate the young master's body,

629
00:40:24,688 --> 00:40:27,823
and see if it can suppress the cold
symptoms in the young master's body.

630
00:40:28,826 --> 00:40:30,795
As for completely detoxifying it...

631
00:40:31,962 --> 00:40:32,962
I'm afraid...

632
00:40:36,066 --> 00:40:37,368
I know what you mean.

633
00:40:40,004 --> 00:40:42,505
You're afraid that in the end
I'll end up with nothing.

634
00:40:43,407 --> 00:40:44,608
But at this point,

635
00:40:45,476 --> 00:40:48,045
there's nothing I can't accept.

636
00:40:52,983 --> 00:40:54,051
Don't worry.

637
00:40:54,852 --> 00:40:56,387
This time I won't run away.

638
00:40:56,821 --> 00:40:58,301
As long as there's a glimmer of hope,

639
00:40:59,123 --> 00:41:00,524
I won't give up.

640
00:42:06,891 --> 00:42:08,492
Is it a letter from the palace?

641
00:42:10,261 --> 00:42:11,262
It says.

642
00:42:11,996 --> 00:42:13,063
Father is seriously ill

643
00:42:13,864 --> 00:42:15,442
and wants me to return
to the capital immediately

644
00:42:15,466 --> 00:42:17,234
to handle government affairs.

645
00:42:18,068 --> 00:42:19,036
But when I left the capital.

646
00:42:19,037 --> 00:42:20,437
Father was clearly fine.

647
00:42:22,673 --> 00:42:24,141
I can't go back now.

648
00:42:24,241 --> 00:42:25,241
A Qi.

649
00:42:26,644 --> 00:42:27,644
Now.

650
00:42:27,878 --> 00:42:29,656
The heavy responsibility
of reorganizing the court

651
00:42:29,680 --> 00:42:30,848
has fallen on to you.

652
00:42:32,149 --> 00:42:33,550
You must go back.

653
00:42:35,352 --> 00:42:36,353
But you...

654
00:42:38,155 --> 00:42:39,155
I...

655
00:42:40,291 --> 00:42:43,394
My body is getting thinner every day.

656
00:42:44,228 --> 00:42:45,563
You've been by my side all along.

657
00:42:46,356 --> 00:42:48,592
Looking into your eyes...

658
00:42:49,700 --> 00:42:52,469
going from hopeful to
increasingly desperate...

659
00:42:53,404 --> 00:42:54,872
is more painful than killing me.

660
00:42:57,841 --> 00:42:58,841
A Qi.

661
00:43:00,444 --> 00:43:01,645
Go back to the palace.

662
00:43:02,880 --> 00:43:04,481
Don't continue to stay with me.

663
00:43:12,156 --> 00:43:13,156
Brother.

664
00:43:13,223 --> 00:43:14,425
How is father's illness?

665
00:43:18,662 --> 00:43:19,663
Father is seriously ill.

666
00:43:19,763 --> 00:43:21,241
And there's no one to oversee the country.

667
00:43:21,265 --> 00:43:21,832
Brother.

668
00:43:21,833 --> 00:43:23,233
We must set off as soon as possible

669
00:43:24,902 --> 00:43:26,003
and return to the capital.

670
00:43:27,237 --> 00:43:28,639
Yanzhi's illness hasn't healed yet.

671
00:43:29,073 --> 00:43:30,139
I can't go back.

672
00:43:30,140 --> 00:43:31,140
A Qi.

673
00:43:36,080 --> 00:43:38,849
How can matters of the country
and the people be taken lightly?

674
00:43:39,116 --> 00:43:40,484
Under the heavens,

675
00:43:41,051 --> 00:43:42,987
countless people are counting on you.

676
00:43:45,356 --> 00:43:46,223
How could I possibly

677
00:43:46,290 --> 00:43:48,250
leave you behind and
return to the capital alone?

678
00:43:48,626 --> 00:43:51,061
Or come back to the capital with me.

679
00:43:51,595 --> 00:43:52,062
Then

680
00:43:52,129 --> 00:43:54,131
I'll find the best doctors to cure you.

681
00:43:55,399 --> 00:43:56,399
Qi'er.

682
00:43:56,834 --> 00:43:57,834
Yanzhi

683
00:43:58,035 --> 00:44:00,604
I was just looking for
you to discuss this matter.

684
00:44:01,405 --> 00:44:04,608
If Yanzhi continues to be
treated in the Central Plains.

685
00:44:06,076 --> 00:44:09,880
I'm afraid he'll end up like Tang'er.

686
00:44:12,349 --> 00:44:13,550
At this point.

687
00:44:14,051 --> 00:44:16,887
We can only take Yanzhi
to Japan and give it a try.

688
00:44:21,558 --> 00:44:22,558
Japan.

689
00:44:23,961 --> 00:44:26,363
I previously sent a letter to Japan

690
00:44:26,816 --> 00:44:28,418
asking my business partners.

691
00:44:28,632 --> 00:44:30,167
I was waiting for a reply.

692
00:44:30,567 --> 00:44:33,070
But now, after thinking it over.

693
00:44:33,270 --> 00:44:35,882
It's better to take advantage of
Yanzhi's still relatively good health.

694
00:44:35,906 --> 00:44:39,043
And let me take him to Japan for treatment.

695
00:44:39,843 --> 00:44:41,745
Perhaps there's still a chance.

696
00:44:46,517 --> 00:44:47,517
Japan.

697
00:44:48,686 --> 00:44:50,487
Amandtuo is a strange poison from Japan.

698
00:44:51,221 --> 00:44:53,791
Perhaps there's a way to detoxify it there.

699
00:44:55,793 --> 00:44:56,593
Yanzhi.

700
00:44:56,594 --> 00:44:57,795
Let's pack our things now.

701
00:44:57,828 --> 00:44:58,828
And hurry to Japan.

702
00:45:04,301 --> 00:45:05,301
A Qi.

703
00:45:06,036 --> 00:45:07,036
You can't go.

704
00:45:08,405 --> 00:45:10,207
You have more important things to do.

705
00:45:14,011 --> 00:45:15,011
Your Highness.

706
00:45:15,412 --> 00:45:17,412
The government affairs
of Daxing can't be delayed.

707
00:45:18,014 --> 00:45:19,950
I know you care deeply
about the young master.

708
00:45:20,744 --> 00:45:23,680
I will go to Japan with the young master

709
00:45:24,955 --> 00:45:27,591
I'll take care of the young
master along the way.

710
00:45:27,825 --> 00:45:29,026
You can rest assured.

711
00:45:33,030 --> 00:45:34,030
Nan Xing.

712
00:45:36,200 --> 00:45:37,835
With Aunt Lin and Doctor Bai,

713
00:45:38,502 --> 00:45:41,839
Accompanying Brother Yanzhi to Japan,
brother, you can rest assured now.

714
00:45:43,073 --> 00:45:43,674
Yes.

715
00:45:43,674 --> 00:45:44,274
Fifth Prince.

716
00:45:44,308 --> 00:45:45,609
You have to trust my aunt.

717
00:45:45,802 --> 00:45:47,206
When she promises something to someone.

718
00:45:47,230 --> 00:45:48,550
She'll definitely make it happen.

719
00:46:14,505 --> 00:46:15,806
What are you thinking about?

720
00:46:20,544 --> 00:46:21,645
I'm thinking about.

721
00:46:23,747 --> 00:46:25,125
The last Mid-Autumn Festival night.

722
00:46:25,149 --> 00:46:26,949
We were supposed to
make wishes by the river.

723
00:46:27,684 --> 00:46:30,287
Unfortunately, it didn't happen.

724
00:46:31,522 --> 00:46:32,762
Later, we made wishes together.

725
00:46:33,557 --> 00:46:34,691
The moon that night

726
00:46:35,893 --> 00:46:38,053
was not as round as it was
on the Mid-Autumn Festival.

727
00:46:38,729 --> 00:46:39,729
Perhaps

728
00:46:40,430 --> 00:46:42,032
the wishes made may not be as effective.

729
00:46:42,859 --> 00:46:43,859
So what?

730
00:46:44,835 --> 00:46:45,969
In the future,

731
00:46:46,703 --> 00:46:48,605
we can set off sky lanterns every day

732
00:46:49,206 --> 00:46:50,326
and make wishes to the moon,

733
00:46:51,008 --> 00:46:52,242
annoying the gods to death

734
00:46:52,676 --> 00:46:54,901
so that they have no choice but to
fulfill our wishes.

735
00:47:01,785 --> 00:47:02,785
A Qi,

736
00:47:02,986 --> 00:47:04,121
why don't we

737
00:47:04,922 --> 00:47:05,922
be together today

738
00:47:05,956 --> 00:47:07,224
and make wishes to the gods

739
00:47:07,324 --> 00:47:08,444
to make up for past regrets?

740
00:47:13,230 --> 00:47:15,766
The believer Yin Qi
makes a wish to the gods,

741
00:47:16,833 --> 00:47:19,269
hoping that the gods will bless my Yanzhi

742
00:47:20,204 --> 00:47:21,204
on his journey to Japan,

743
00:47:21,271 --> 00:47:22,272
to return cured

744
00:47:23,240 --> 00:47:26,410
and stay by my side forever,

745
00:47:27,444 --> 00:47:29,044
spending the rest of our lives together.

746
00:47:37,087 --> 00:47:38,087
God,

747
00:47:39,590 --> 00:47:40,691
please bless

748
00:47:40,724 --> 00:47:42,226
my A Qi

749
00:47:43,827 --> 00:47:45,362
to live safely.

750
00:47:59,509 --> 00:48:01,510
The true god in heaven,

751
00:48:01,511 --> 00:48:04,747
A Qi and I love each other deeply,

752
00:48:04,748 --> 00:48:06,850
yet we cannot grow old together.

753
00:48:08,752 --> 00:48:11,354
If you truly have power,

754
00:48:11,355 --> 00:48:12,521
please bless the man I
love deeply before me

755
00:48:12,522 --> 00:48:14,458
that he may no longer suffer

756
00:48:15,959 --> 00:48:19,062
and live in peace and
prosperity in the future.

757
00:48:19,122 --> 00:48:21,224
May he be safe and well.

758
00:49:45,511 --> 00:49:48,098
(Three years later)

759
00:50:02,766 --> 00:50:04,001
I say, Miss,

760
00:50:04,234 --> 00:50:08,171
It's fine that you gave gave that wine ordered
by Mr. Zhang to Mr. Li to drink yesterday,

761
00:50:08,271 --> 00:50:09,438
but after the wine was finished,

762
00:50:09,439 --> 00:50:11,250
you didn't even go to the wine shop
to buy more to replenish it.

763
00:50:11,274 --> 00:50:12,285
If you continue to do business like this,

764
00:50:12,308 --> 00:50:14,508
my Yanbo Tower will close
down sooner rather than later.

765
00:50:15,012 --> 00:50:16,213
I know I was wrong.

766
00:50:16,313 --> 00:50:17,480
I'll have Duan Yi and Duan Yong

767
00:50:17,481 --> 00:50:19,349
go buy the wine and make it up to you.

768
00:50:24,154 --> 00:50:24,955
Does my Lin family lack

769
00:50:24,956 --> 00:50:26,590
a few jars of wine like this?

770
00:50:26,623 --> 00:50:27,824
This isn't about the wine.

771
00:50:29,092 --> 00:50:30,394
It's not about the wine.

772
00:50:30,961 --> 00:50:31,961
What is it then?

773
00:50:32,662 --> 00:50:33,030
Your Highness.

774
00:50:33,030 --> 00:50:33,797
Your Highness.

775
00:50:33,797 --> 00:50:34,264
Elder brother.

776
00:50:34,331 --> 00:50:35,332
What brings you here?

777
00:50:37,234 --> 00:50:38,001
What's the matter?

778
00:50:38,001 --> 00:50:38,969
I came to see you.

779
00:50:38,993 --> 00:50:39,993
Aren't I welcome?

780
00:50:40,303 --> 00:50:41,004
Welcome, welcome.

781
00:50:41,004 --> 00:50:42,004
Of course I welcome you.

782
00:50:42,406 --> 00:50:44,017
How long do you plan to
stay in Jiangnan this time?

783
00:50:44,041 --> 00:50:45,742
I'll prepare a guest room right away.

784
00:50:45,909 --> 00:50:46,510
No hurry.

785
00:50:46,510 --> 00:50:47,077
Heshu,

786
00:50:47,077 --> 00:50:47,711
this time,

787
00:50:48,078 --> 00:50:49,598
I don't plan to return to the capital.

788
00:50:51,481 --> 00:50:52,481
Really, elder brother?

789
00:50:52,649 --> 00:50:53,884
You're not lying to me, right?

790
00:50:54,151 --> 00:50:54,351
You...

791
00:50:54,751 --> 00:50:56,253
How did you persuade Father Emperor?

792
00:50:57,320 --> 00:50:59,289
Seventh brother has
improved a lot this year.

793
00:51:00,309 --> 00:51:02,145
He's now fully-fledged

794
00:51:02,378 --> 00:51:03,946
and can handle things on his own.

795
00:51:04,761 --> 00:51:06,430
Since I've completed my mission,

796
00:51:06,830 --> 00:51:08,832
Father Emperor naturally couldn't stop me.

797
00:51:10,233 --> 00:51:11,568
That's wonderful.

798
00:51:11,701 --> 00:51:12,701
Xianyue,

799
00:51:13,003 --> 00:51:15,238
Tonight, I'll throw a grand banquet

800
00:51:15,272 --> 00:51:17,752
and invite my brother to taste
all the delicacies of Jiangnan.

801
00:51:17,808 --> 00:51:18,608
No problem.

802
00:51:18,632 --> 00:51:19,900
Just put it on your tab.

803
00:51:23,447 --> 00:51:24,948
Seeing you doing so well,

804
00:51:25,248 --> 00:51:26,650
I can rest assured.

805
00:51:30,554 --> 00:51:33,957
After that, I want to
go to Talhan again.

806
00:51:36,827 --> 00:51:37,827
Brother...

807
00:51:38,028 --> 00:51:38,795
You...

808
00:51:38,795 --> 00:51:39,795
Actually, I...

809
00:51:43,333 --> 00:51:44,333
I know.

810
00:51:44,968 --> 00:51:47,771
Aunt Lin was afraid I
would fall into despair

811
00:51:47,804 --> 00:51:48,804
and never recover.

812
00:51:49,106 --> 00:51:52,008
So she did everything she
could to take Yanzhi away.

813
00:51:54,344 --> 00:51:55,479
In these three years,

814
00:51:56,112 --> 00:51:57,581
I've been thinking every day

815
00:51:57,948 --> 00:51:59,508
about the moments I shared with Yanzhi,

816
00:52:00,650 --> 00:52:01,650
remembering him

817
00:52:03,253 --> 00:52:04,554
and every word he said to me,

818
00:52:04,788 --> 00:52:06,389
saying he would always be by my side.

819
00:52:08,492 --> 00:52:10,012
Actually, he didn't break his promise.

820
00:52:10,527 --> 00:52:11,828
In my heart,

821
00:52:12,562 --> 00:52:14,030
he has always been with me.

822
00:52:17,167 --> 00:52:19,035
This time, when I go to Talhan,

823
00:52:20,403 --> 00:52:22,243
afterwards I'll go to Japan to find him again.

824
00:52:25,542 --> 00:52:26,610
Sister Aruna

825
00:52:26,810 --> 00:52:28,210
wrote to say she's getting married.

826
00:52:28,478 --> 00:52:28,845
Brother,

827
00:52:28,846 --> 00:52:31,248
you can go in Yanzhi's
place to see her off.

828
00:52:51,261 --> 00:52:52,261
Yanzhi...

829
00:52:53,036 --> 00:52:54,747
I can't believe that
in the blink of an eye,

830
00:52:54,771 --> 00:52:56,173
three years have passed so quickly.

831
00:52:57,340 --> 00:52:58,241
The events of my past life

832
00:52:58,242 --> 00:52:59,643
are almost fading from my memory.

833
00:53:00,990 --> 00:53:02,858
Since the gods have given us this chance

834
00:53:03,013 --> 00:53:04,213
to meet again,

835
00:53:04,214 --> 00:53:06,082
why do they have to keep us apart?

836
00:53:07,250 --> 00:53:08,250
Yanzhi...

837
00:53:08,852 --> 00:53:10,220
Whether you're alive or dead,

838
00:53:10,720 --> 00:53:12,588
even if you're in the underworld,

839
00:53:12,589 --> 00:53:14,724
I'll find you.

840
00:53:15,084 --> 00:53:17,186
Even if the gods try to stop us,

841
00:53:17,594 --> 00:53:19,529
as long as I don't give up,

842
00:53:20,397 --> 00:53:22,265
what can they do to me?

843
00:54:32,502 --> 00:54:33,637
Yanzhi...

844
00:54:35,405 --> 00:54:36,640
You're mine.

845
00:54:43,246 --> 00:54:44,848
When will you finally admit

846
00:54:46,750 --> 00:54:47,751
your feelings for me?

847
00:55:23,779 --> 00:55:33,266
(The End)
